{"id": "1228042346289954877", "channel_id": "1228042346289954877", "type": 0, "author_id": "1112189464140324947", "author_name": "timee_ky", "author_bot": false, "content": "3-1 boos是不会停歇的小蜜蜂，所以带了惩戒来堆死扛，西莱来拖一回合抗伤。留着易伤刻印拖过六回合可以四大全开对轴杀\n\n3-2 boos是两只，用了希莉，拖过六回合报偿杀一个破链杀一个\n\n3-3 叠毒杀，艾瑞卡带欢宴很硬boos没什么生存难度，主要道中可能压力会大一些。\n\n3-4 神父有着强大的生存性能并且可以很好的克制尤乌（抗单段伤害，血池解流血）安心叠苍白回旋，死扛爆了就用一下因菲特大招\n\n3-5 国家队碾压，白银差分机可以解放算力，幸运观众因为墨菲牌权很高可以给到墨菲。衰竭刻印有奇效，抽牌刻印对差分机来说也很有用。", "timestamp": "2024-04-11T18:01:51.279000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-04-11T18:44:35.098000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 6}], "attachments": [{"id": "1228042347087138907", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-04-12-02-00-00-467_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 197149, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1228042346289954877/1228042347087138907/Screenshot_2024-04-12-02-00-00-467_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69cc0c0f&is=69caba8f&hm=5049a1fb65cacf41ad009cde39442b2ca300c5ff0c4846b0083be9d6f9e3501c&"}, {"id": "1228042347976069130", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-04-12-02-00-04-827_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 195937, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1228042346289954877/1228042347976069130/Screenshot_2024-04-12-02-00-04-827_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69cc0c0f&is=69caba8f&hm=d22ab9460be83bf0773e0e8f588997337bea4af54d28dea21e9a42c6ed5f6b96&"}, {"id": "1228042348567593013", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-04-12-02-00-10-350_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 236772, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1228042346289954877/1228042348567593013/Screenshot_2024-04-12-02-00-10-350_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69cc0c0f&is=69caba8f&hm=f873531e6098a09980cd332e9424f5ecbe53c5c8e27e9c7145e8f1af79623515&"}, {"id": "1228042349188481154", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-04-12-02-00-12-931_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "imag