{"id": "1228042670962638930", "channel_id": "1228042346289954877", "type": 4, "author_id": "1112189464140324947", "author_name": "timee_ky", "author_bot": false, "content": "容灾350配队攻略", "timestamp": "2024-04-11T18:03:08.687000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1228042346289954877", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "容灾350配队攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1227516925479747584", "1181143392739147778"]}
{"id": "1227998880449429556", "channel_id": "1227998880449429556", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "第6期「融災禁區」地圖。\n◆每兩週刷新獎勵與關卡，每個關卡只需要完成普通模式、困難或癲狂模式其中之一。\n◆經過毒地板（紫色格子）時，會扣除 血量上限 的約5%，也就是固定值。當踏入毒地板所扣除的血量被判斷爲致命傷害，則觸發死亡抵抗/復活確認。\n◆同一關卡的Ⅰ級警報和Ⅱ級警報的地圖相同，Ⅲ級警報也相同。\n▼▼▼\n【第1波】特遣記錄 - 索蕾爾「薔薇禮讚」-飲酒歌 地圖\n【第2波】特遣記錄 - 達芙黛爾「雨鎮幽影」-暴雨將至 地圖\n【第3波】意識潛游 - 艾瑞卡「扭曲核心」-聲音如是說 地圖\n【第4波】意識潛游 - 珊「如歌的雕琢」-珊瑚女之死 地圖\n【第5波】幻夢深淺 - 莉莉「淤泥之花」地圖\n\nuid100001547", "timestamp": "2024-04-11T15:09:08.215000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 6}], "attachments": [{"id": "1227998880755617892", "filename": "Image_1712847722869.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 281815, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1227998880449429556/1227998880755617892/Image_1712847722869.jpg?ex=69cbe394&is=69ca9214&hm=cffc126adf6cf397a0304332435b099a931c00dff3c7f384ad3c5d17f84ed0ce&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1227998880449429556", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "第6期「融災禁區」地圖總覽", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1227516925479747584", "1181143392739147778"]}
{"id": "1227809640566226944", "channel_id": "1227809640566226944", "type": 0, "author_id": "1112189464140324947", "author_name": "timee_ky", "author_bot": false, "content": "大家好我是Timee，是个笨蛋深海玩家。4-11日日更新了新的容灾，打完5-3后写一下自己的心得，如果有不对的地方见谅我也尽可能及时改正，感谢大家收看！", "timestamp": "2024-04-11T02:37:09.911000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-04-11T02:54:52.051000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [{"id": "1227809640834793552", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-04-11-10-30-55-194_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 310496, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1227809640566226944/1227809640834793552/Screenshot_2024-04-11-10-30-55-194_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69cbdc15&is=69ca8a95&hm=e14666aa0001e267d4ad44504c977cf6e6ecfb5a3143eb64459bce60414bd627&"}, {"id": "1227809641182924810", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-04-11-10-31-11-180_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 175350, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1227809640566226944/1227809641182924810/Screenshot_2024-04-11-10-31-11-180_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69cbdc16&is=69ca8a96&hm=802aa26387f66aa7ae2a9f5b71c39f75c9c495b71242f724d1c0c0b00e6c965e&"}, {"id": "1227809641493168138", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-04-11-10-34-32-387_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 240403, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1227809640566226944/1227809641493168138/Screenshot_2024-04-11-10-34-32-387_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69cbdc16&is=69ca8a96&hm=a75e54b19d3f3191a81dd47919ed942613fb23b8c5a09e708a038c3644da87ad&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1227809640566226944", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "容灾5-3魔术师深海配队与打法", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1227516925479747584", "1181143392739147778", "1174179716706619494"]}
{"id": "1227813045137444945", "channel_id": "1227809640566226944", "type": 0, "author_id": "1112189464140324947", "author_name": "timee_ky", "author_bot": false, "content": "道中：精英是寄主，会招小怪，主要就是叠献祭去杀\n\nboos：主要机制是选择一名召唤体做幸运观众，这名召唤体打牌可以降低boos的伤害但是也会降低自己的最大血量上限。我个人是把幸运观众给了墨菲，因为墨菲的牌权很高，不要吝啬血上限尽管出牌就是。\n\n造物：建议七鳃鳗，如果可以的话补一个圣腕会打的更快，如果没圣腕可以补防御类造物。\n\n命轮：建议图鲁带个灯塔黑子，因为boos攻击手法有多段伤害，降低攻击是很不错的选择\n\n刻印：建议衰竭或者抽牌，这关有白银差分机所以抽牌是很不错的选择", "timestamp": "2024-04-11T02:50:41.624000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1227809640566226944", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "容灾5-3魔术师深海配队与打法", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1227516925479747584", "1181143392739147778", "1174179716706619494"]}
